{"tha-ap69:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap69:0.2":"Sakacintaniyavagga ","tha-ap69:0.3":"Vatthadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap69:1.1":"“Pakkhijato tada asim, ","tha-ap69:1.2":"supanno garuladhipo; ","tha-ap69:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap69:1.4":"gacchantam gandhamadanam. ","tha-ap69:2.1":"Jahitva garulavannam, ","tha-ap69:2.2":"manavakam adharayim; ","tha-ap69:2.3":"Ekam vattham maya dinnam, ","tha-ap69:2.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap69:3.1":"Tanca dussam patiggayha, ","tha-ap69:3.2":"buddho lokagganayako; ","tha-ap69:3.3":"Antalikkhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap69:3.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap69:4.1":"‘Imina vatthadanena, ","tha-ap69:4.2":"cittassa panidhihi ca; ","tha-ap69:4.3":"Pahaya garulam yonim, ","tha-ap69:4.4":"devaloke ramissati’. ","tha-ap69:5.1":"Atthadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap69:5.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap69:5.3":"Vatthadanam pasamsitva, ","tha-ap69:5.4":"pakkami uttaramukho. ","tha-ap69:6.1":"Bhave nibbattamanamhi, ","tha-ap69:6.2":"honti me vatthasampada; ","tha-ap69:6.3":"Akase chadanam hoti, ","tha-ap69:6.4":"vatthadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap69:7.1":"Arunava satta jana, ","tha-ap69:7.2":"cakkavatti mahabbala; ","tha-ap69:7.3":"Chattimsatimhi asimsu, ","tha-ap69:7.4":"kappamhi manujadhipa. ","tha-ap69:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap69:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap69:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap69:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vatthadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap69:10.1":"Vatthadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}